<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#acs57">Is chaos theory useful in the social sciences?</A><P>
<LI><A HREF="#acs50">Has there been any progress in developing fairer ways for people to vote?</A><P>
<LI><A HREF="#q8">Where does the measurement of the "meter" come from?</A><P> 
<LI><A HREF="#q11">How does a laser measure the speed of a car?</A><P> 
