<P>
<a href="http://www.oup-usa.org/docs/019510109X.html">THE MONKEY WARS</a>. Deborah Blum. Oxford University Press, 1994.
<P>
THE ANIMAL RESEARCH CONTROVERSY: PROTEST, PROCESS AND PUBLIC POLICY. Andrew N. Rowan and Franklin M. Loew, with Joan C. Weer. Center for Animals and Public Policy, Tufts University School of Veterinary Medicine, 1995.
