<A HREF="0297massonnetbox1.html"><IMG SRC="IMG/massonnet1sm.gif" ALT="CLICK HERE TO SEE INTERFERENCE FRINGES" ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH="150" HEIGHT="188" BORDER="0"></A>

