<td><BR><center><H1>Global Climatic Change <BR>on Mars</H1>
<B>Today a frozen world, <BR>Mars at one time may have had <BR>more temperate conditions,
<BR>with flowing rivers, thawing seas, <BR>melting glaciers and, perhaps, <BR>abundant
life</B></center>
<P><I><A HREF="#author">by Jeffrey S. Kargel and Robert G. Strom</A></I>
</td></tr></table>
<TABLE BORDER=0 VALIGN=TOP width=476>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=120>
<IMG SRC="../graphics/vertwhiteline.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT width="8" height="6650">
<P><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2">
