<A HREF="#2">An Ocean Away</A>
<BR><IMG SRC="../graphics/arrowsmall.gif" ALIGN=TOP>
<A HREF="#3">Trust the Old Salts</A>
<BR><IMG SRC="../graphics/arrowsmall.gif" ALIGN=TOP>
<A HREF="#4">Turning on the Heat</A>
<P><B>SIDEBAR:</B>
